{"tid":222170,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"棍van點樣可以減慢車速而又唔停車","createTime":"2017-04-29T10:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T16:02:44.000Z","uid":88707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ae77ee4007335d50afcd5624cc04f0c6956efc","tid":222170,"uid":88707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"黎緊考天光道， 其中一條路線係上斜+讓路黎， 點樣可以令車速慢而又唔係停哂， 我而家係踩少break,  速度係慢左少少， 但未睇哂2 邊架車已經出左路口， 踩深少少break又驚會死火， 如break +離合咁踩， 係咪最好拉埋手掣，做正常停車， 以防一開車就溜後。 Thanks"},{"pid":"a2f7e3db15b75123e17ebdcd568861543b20f009","tid":222170,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"吊定極力子?"},{"pid":"066d97960b08338e0c0bf2fd462c9ce20458f1c8","tid":222170,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"讓路唔洗急 <br />\n技術未到 一定要停哂 加 手制<br />\n做多次開車動作 拎頭 吊極力子"},{"pid":"32a48088f47784812415504e2a816fbd9aa4293d","tid":222170,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"減慢車速唔停車咪得囉"},{"pid":"70f4ae9737de86caf70e44cd06e75705244489ae","tid":222170,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"老遠見到迴旋處 hi一hi brake 再拖波"},{"pid":"2272e5edc09041ca3240e764ed586faed88fe5fe","tid":222170,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"驚死火咪落波<br />\n<br />\n無得再落就吊離合器"},{"pid":"8ee9af280582086d7dff91868e5ae7e1b33ad10f","tid":222170,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"考車就停晒架車啦<br />\n望清楚兩邊先再出車"},{"pid":"706c77fdf8e28dd476ab2efc9cc7bf749b3ebcc6","tid":222170,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"上斜慢慢放油門已經好慢架啦 唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c41576fecc5e31bfa0ca91c711b649c34b5f5f","tid":222170,"uid":60840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"江蘇街出返靠背壟道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰陣都係推1波唔比油，部車自己碌上去"},{"pid":"53cfb4239f7e076638c1019cf68841e6ff508a61","tid":222170,"uid":60840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"通常左右兩邊都有死車，極力子 brake停定等都得<br />\n如果多車就可以拉手制空波等"},{"pid":"8ebbbea018dda36db326a872bb2f1b5394cf8a64","tid":222170,"uid":91309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"果條我記得唔算好鈄既路？如果係既話應該係用1-2波行。開始上鈄可以比大小小油，之後輕力踩由佢流前，到讓車位停車。重新做過基本野再開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢黎最緊要唔好急"},{"pid":"e1b300127e3b36ec73f122131d788f2d5f535c8f","tid":222170,"uid":26168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"一路吊住比少少油流前囉，不過你學緊車我驚你掌握唔到大油得劑聞到𤓓味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做返全套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70262ac899152dc75f48190ee6421917c658b5fe","tid":222170,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊考天光道， 其中一條路線係上斜+讓路黎， 點樣可以令車速慢而又唔係停哂， 我而家係踩少break,  速度係慢左少少， 但未睇哂2 邊架車已經出左路口， 踩深少少break又驚會死火， 如break +離合咁踩， 係咪最好拉埋手掣，做正常停車， 以防一開車就溜後。 Thanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落一波慢慢碌過去，一波既速度係可以慢過你行路"},{"pid":"86042479ebc79fa7ca26703344356ac571425bff","tid":222170,"uid":42110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊考天光道， 其中一條路線係上斜+讓路黎， 點樣可以令車速慢而又唔係停哂， 我而家係踩少break,  速度係慢左少少， 但未睇哂2 邊架車已經出左路口， 踩深少少break又驚會死火， 如break +離合咁踩， 係咪最好拉埋手掣，做正常停車， 以防一開車就溜後。 Thanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落一波慢慢碌過去，一波既速度係可以慢過你行路</blockquote><br />\n哩個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踩少少Brake 轉落一波 吊極力子<br />\n咁樣都已經可以好慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果好似樓主咁講<br />\nBreak ＋ Brake 再拉手掣<br />\n後面啲車一定屌柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd673855b6de13e87c91f8668ff3efcf33a23efc","tid":222170,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"拖低波"},{"pid":"93f73b35947e0970a0ffc2def7d9864106187bfc","tid":222170,"uid":61414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"讓路一定吊住極力子<br />\n因為你唔會知道要讓幾耐，同埋你考緊牌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個過程:<br />\n見到讓路牌: 剎車面，慢車<br />\n就來到讓路牌: 落埋極力子<br />\n到讓路牌: 重剎車，可停或龜速<br />\n睇路況，無車可出就: 起返摩擦點 打燈擰頭俾油鬆極力子 一氣呵成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出唔到住:踩死剎車，等超過10秒拉埋手制<br />\n (記得如果長期踩極力子剎車，但唔拉手制，都係有問題，有錯指正)"},{"pid":"6ff792244e7b1076d1831af62b0facf7c300c446","tid":222170,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"依啲嘢係講經驗 俾啲心機"},{"pid":"866030173f4b772f03419c26d27cc643bac0826b","tid":222170,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"重係學神就咪撚貪快啦<br />\n有讓路牌老虎蟹都停車<br />\n望兩邊打燈出<br />\n我係考官見你唔停實 dup重 break肥你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86daa414b99d39c54c27aa8f852113ee59365d8","tid":222170,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:02:44.000Z","msg":"講經驗嘅 俾啲心機 好快考到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cr5gj73h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcr5gj73h&h=5f4eb251&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}